Step-by-Step Execution in Exam
✅ STEP 1 — Create New Project

Open Android Studio → New Project
Select Empty Activity
Name: WebViewDemo
Package: com.example.webviewdemo
Language: Java
Min SDK: API 21
Click Finish → Wait for Gradle


✅ STEP 2 — Add INTERNET Permission in AndroidManifest.xml

Go to: app → manifests → AndroidManifest.xml
Add before <application> tag:

xml<uses-permission android:name="android.permission.INTERNET"/>
⚠️ Without this, app will show blank white screen — most common mistake!

✅ STEP 3 — Edit activity_main.xml

Go to: res → layout → activity_main.xml
Click Code tab → Replace everything with XML below


✅ STEP 4 — Edit MainActivity.java

Go to: java → com.example.webviewdemo → MainActivity
Replace everything with Java code below


✅ STEP 5 — Run the App

Click Run ▶️ → Select emulator → OK
Make sure emulator has internet access
Type URL → Click Go → Website loads!
